channel.title: Help! no class files in my server
channel.description: ok in my new server i got there is no class files anywhere, so i need to decompile them, but i want a good one, not the ones you open with Cavaj then asks you to decompile them, i want one like a normal complier that just decomplies class files. is that possible? [br][br][size=1]Posted on: July 30, 2009, 06:49:18 am[/size][hr]i mean like you see if you want to delete all Java files, there is a code in the compiler that tells it to like *del instead of deleting them i want to decompile the .class files into java files. Or is the a good decompiler that decompilers all class files not just by 1 by 1 that is so long.
